
** scanimage

  <example>
    # default is gray
    $ scanimage --resolution 300 > out.pnm
    $ scanimage --mode color --resolution 300 \
       -l 0 -t 0 -x 210 -y 297 > out.pnm
  </example>


  - see to man *sane-epson*.
  - see to scan.sh
  - see to convert.sh

** convert

  <example>
    $ convert --page 595x842 out.pnm out.pdf
  </example>

** sizes

<example>
  A4    : 595x842
  Letter: 612x792
</example>

** mm to pts

  - pts = size in mm / 25.4 * 72

** scan to pdf

  - MyScanPdf
